1. Receiver Dish (Antena) : 9.6jt

2. Langganan Bulanan :
  
    -  Paket Standard : 1.9jt/bln

   -  Paket Mobile : 2.4jt/bln

   -  Paket Mobile Priority :
     . 50GB : 4jt/bln

     . 5TB : 80jt/bln


1. Paket Standard :
   - Kecepatan : 30-150 Mbps.
   - Prioritas Data : Lebih rendah paket Mobile Priority.
   -  Tujuan : Cocok rumah tangga bisnis.
   -  Ketidakterbatasan : Data tak terbatas, kecepatan berkurang jaringan sibuk.

2. Paket Mobile :
   -  Kecepatan : 40-220 Mbps.
   -  Prioritas Data : Lebih tinggi paket Standard.
   -  Tujuan : Cocok bisnis bergerak, truk, bus, klinik kesehatan bergerak.
   -  Ketidakterbatasan : Data tak terbatas, ada penurunan kecepatan kuota tertentu.

3.  Paket Mobile Priority :
   -  Kecepatan : 40-220 Mbps.
   -  Prioritas Data : Tertinggi.
   -  Tujuan : Cocok bisnis bergerak sektor publik (darurat, kapal, lainnya).
   -  Ketidakterbatasan : Paket data disebutkan (50 GB, 1 TB, 5 TB) bukan batas keras. Jika melebihi kuota, Anda dapat menggunakan data dasar batasan berada daratan. Namun, di laut, Anda dapat membeli data prioritas tambahan.

- Standard Package: 1.9 million/month

- Mobile Package: 2.4 million/month

- Mobile Priority Package:
.50GB: 4 million/month

- Speed: 30-150 Mbps.
- Data Priority: Lower Mobile Priority Package.
- Purpose: Suitable business households.

Comment:
sebenarnya empat kekurangan internet satelit starlink :

1. Internet satelit starlink dapat terpengaruh kondisi cuaca, jadi kalo misalnya cuacanya bagus koneksi internetnya bakal terganggu

2. Internet satelit starlink cocok digunakan bermain game kompetitif karna pingnya tidak se-stabil internet kabel

3. Harga paket internet satelit starlink sangat mahal dimulai 750 ribu hingga 86 juta rupiah, bahkan kalo mau beli modem router & antena satelit starlink website resminya bayarnya pake kartu kredit, masyarakat tinggal daerah terpencil punya kartu kredit sama sekali

4. Router internet starlink tidak punya port LAN menghubungkan komputer wifi extender, jadi mau tidak mau kita harus membeli kabel adaptor erthernet menghubungkan kabel LAN router komputer wifi extender, harga kabel adaptor erternet sangat mahal sekali
Translated_Comment:
Actually four shortcomings of Starlink satellite internet:

1. Starlink satellite internet can be affected by weather conditions, so if for example the weather is good internet connection will be disturbed

2. Starlink Satellite Internet is suitable for playing competitive games because the ping is not as stable as internet cable

3. The price of Starlink satellite internet package is very expensive starting at 750 thousand to 86 million rupiah, even if you want to buy a starlink router & satellite modem, the official website pays using a credit card, the public lives a remote area has a credit card at all

4. Starlink Internet Router does not have a LAN port connecting WiFi Extender Computer, so inevitably we have to buy an Erthernet adapter cable connecting the WiFi Extender Computer Router LAN cable, the price of an eRternet adapter cable is very expensive

Ukuran piringan mempengaruhi jumlah bandwidth ditampung, paling besar 2.4 meter nampung bandwidth 2 Mbps dedicated 1:1, koneksinya stabil kuat cuaca.
Sedangkan kecil 1.2 meter sharing bandwidth 5 -15 Mbps bahkan lebih itu, rentan cuaca kalo misalkan hujan sinyalnya satelitnya hilang, ditambah yang pake FUP lagi, kalo udah abis FUP nya koneksinya makin lemotnya minta ampun.ğŸ˜‚

Lah Starlink pointing, cukup scan satelit yang ada langit, colokin power listrik dah nyala lagi bandwithnya kecepatannya bisa ratusan Mbps. ğŸ˜‚
Emang keren sih teknologi.


Btw thanks bagi yang udah baca sampe abis, sukses selalu buat kali semua ğŸ˜

A little story, I used to be a vsat technician, for example, for example, divided by 12:43 - 12:50, the shape of the disk is small in the divideo is also big, on average if the sample is a small size of 1.2 meters, if a large size is 1.8 meters to 2.4 meters.

The size of the disk affects the number of bandwidth is accommodated, the biggest 2.4 meters of 2 Mbps dedicated bandwidth 1: 1, the connection is stable.
While the small 1.2 meter sharing bandwidth 5 -15 Mbps even more, vulnerable to the weather if for example the satellite rains are gone, plus those who use the FUP again, if the FUP is after the connection is getting slow to ask for forgiveness.
